00:14:29.696 --> 00:14:31.136
It's that piece.

00:14:30.976 --> 00:14:33.888
It's wrestling with that in our hearts.

00:14:34.688 --> 00:14:36.416
It's surrendering to him.

00:14:36.672 --> 00:14:38.624
It's fixing our eyes on him.

00:14:40.576 --> 00:14:42.336
And it's being peacemakers.

00:14:43.072 --> 00:14:44.192
Pray with me.

00:14:44.320 --> 00:14:46.912
Lord Jesus, Prince of Peace, we come before you.

00:14:47.104 --> 00:14:49.824
Today acknowledging our need for your peace.

00:14:50.688 --> 00:14:52.896
In a world that feels so restless

00:14:53.792 --> 00:14:56.224
Help us to find our rest in you.

00:14:56.704 --> 00:14:59.584
Teach us to surrender our fears and anxieties.

00:14:59.904 --> 00:15:01.600
To trust in your goodness

00:15:01.472 --> 00:15:02.720
And to walk

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:04.224
As your peacemakers.

00:15:04.448 --> 00:15:07.840
Fill our hearts with your peace that surpasses understanding.

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:09.856
And use us.

00:15:09.632 --> 00:15:11.104
To bring your light

00:15:11.072 --> 00:15:12.608
And love to the world

00:15:12.864 --> 00:15:15.776
It is in Jesus' powerful name that I pray.

00:15:16.224 --> 00:15:17.120
Amen.
